result.execSummary:
The defendant Kaphree Ahjanee Jordan was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Kaphree Ahjanee Jordan is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Kaphree Ahjanee Jordan was found guilty of Battery, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 940.19(1).
  • Kaphree Ahjanee Jordan was found guilty of Battery [Modifiers: PTAC, as a Party to a Crime], a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 940.19(1).
